Class Asset

  • java.lang.Object
    • treeParts.ds.Asset
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BUILDING, DTS_kiosk, DTS_murovana, DTS_stoziarova, HV_field, HV_trafo, MV_field, NN_izolovane, NN_vedenie, OWN_CONSUMPTION, PROTECTIONS, VN_beton, VN_drevo, VN_ocel, VN_olej, VN_plast, VVN_cable, VVN_stoziar, VVN_vedenie

    public abstract class Asset
extends java.lang.Object
    This abstract class represents all assets in the hierarchy. It contains all necessary features that all assets in the tree must contain. The features are: price, ratio, metric, planned finance, additional finance and amound of asset.
